- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper involves analyzing the behavior of a complex data structure (timed Petri nets) and computing optimal costs.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with modeling and analyzing a system, which is a common theme in AI research.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper involves formal modeling and analysis, which is a common theme in programming language research.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with a system (Petri nets) and its behavior, which is a common theme in systems and control research.
